                <article>
                    <section id="articleContent" class="article-content">
                        <div class="display-content">
                            <p>好的，橘子君又来给大家投喂狗粮了。</p>
<p>有个网红被求婚上了热搜话题▼</p>
<img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/7baf9b46ffed4ced8c352f04fbcfaca1.jpeg" width="750" height="259" class="content-image">
<p>认识一下今天的故事主人公，一句话概括就是两个毕业于同济大学的高颜值＋学霸＋网红的情侣即将步入婚姻殿堂。</p>
<p>女主人公庄庄，长得很好看没错▼</p>
<img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/a37b9d8f09b343ccbf5738927e428b4b.jpeg" width="1024" height="1024" class="content-image">
<p>拍照风格大概和你日常见到的网红都没有差别</p>
<img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/5d54871c0bee408e9551c2bb0203199f.jpeg" width="1024" height="1024" class="content-image">
                        </div>
                            <section class="look-all" id="artLookAll" data-spm-acode="3402">
                                <em>展开剩余</em><em class="hidden-ratio-num">93</em><em>%</em><i class="icon-fold icon"></i>
                            </section>
                            <div class="hidden-content hide">
                                <p><img width="1024" height="1024" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/cb279dd7c4b34a2e929c96394999fa3c.jpeg"></p>
<p><img width="1024" height="1024" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/5e71412983044aa7aa108d0bb3e0939d.jpeg"></p>
<p>男主人公老尚，可能比一般男孩子更会拍照一点。</p>
<p><img width="1024" height="1024" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/4f6877d7304b4badb045483a6911637b.jpeg"></p>
<p><img width="1024" height="1024" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/886ddeb915bf42da813eb8a25febd7cf.jpeg"></p>
<p>非要说自己长得像井柏然</p>
<p><img width="1279" height="852" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/fffe36ebedd34305b7205ef563633a2a.jpeg"></p>
<p>昨天晚上，男孩子向女孩子求婚了。</p>
<p><img width="749" height="654" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/eb6d1e5f8ee64fb19081a45f867c7c25.jpeg"></p>
<p><img width="750" height="193" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/8669770ca79a4811a02bbe1c22bcd935.jpeg"></p>
<p>求婚现场也是相当浪漫了，气球、烟花、下跪、戒指，什么都有。</p>
<p><img width="350" height="338" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/1aba02f9c2a2444db933611b3529255a.gif"></p>
<p><img width="350" height="338" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/bf42003bb0d44212bce4d4c523a4d732.gif"></p>
<p>女孩子讲：</p>
<p>“我有时候不开心的时候也会想</p>
<p>以后可能我不要嫁给老尚啦</p>
<p>我要嫁给一个比他还高还帅还有钱的男孩子</p>
<p>今天以后虽然老尚还是很傻很幼稚</p>
<p>但是也是没有再比他更想用力爱我的男孩子啦”</p>
<p><img width="750" height="969" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/d998d8d2e4b3453da2b157523e75642f.jpeg"></p>
<p>庄庄的原名是庄舒淇，老尚的原名是尚煦哲，两个人都毕业于同济大学。</p>
<p><img width="750" height="365" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/2908a302d8e64d15be2eaf9d1d7cec53.jpeg"></p>
<p><img width="750" height="592" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/2b5ff841530a4226b705679193c66446.jpeg"></p>
<p>想想人家的出生时间，他们都要结婚了，而我在写同龄人的结婚稿件。</p>
<p><img width="580" height="549" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/c7361ee72f9440bca2b003f320158ca2.jpeg"></p>
<p>两个人从大学开始谈恋爱，具体时间应该是2016年5月。</p>
<p>长得好看是什么感受：</p>
<p>3月在喊单身汪▼</p>
<p><img width="750" height="350" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/d062c627c3f948a1840fc092e5d6f521.jpeg"></p>
<p>4月在喊想谈恋爱▼</p>
<p><img width="750" height="434" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/a720aa8c0c7444bd8f6744010ee1166d.jpeg"></p>
<p>5月开始秀恩爱▼</p>
<p><img width="750" height="426" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/7c6f8d90e3604613bc00428df5784907.jpeg"></p>
<p>在一起以后的第一个生日，老尚记录了两人怎么在一起：</p>
<p>他第一次看到她的照片虎躯一震，干净漂亮开朗爱笑，然后就开始了追逐她的脚步。</p>
<p><img width="1024" height="1591" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/b47df47b7e8f456c9806b2db0b5f9ffa.jpeg"></p>
<p>接着开始施展他拙劣的撩妹技能，讲真，真的很拙劣：</p>
<p>对话一：</p>
<p>“你有男朋友嘛”</p>
<p>“没有啊哈哈哈哈”</p>
<p>“太好了哈哈哈”</p>
<p>对话二：</p>
<p>“都是一米多 彼此彼此”</p>
<p>“你没听说吗，160.3和181.8最配”</p>
<p>“你181.8哦”</p>
<p>“你真的很聪明 就是我”</p>
<p>对话三：</p>
<p>“你是95的？”</p>
<p>“嗯嗯 95”</p>
<p>“你得问一下我啊 嗯嗯 我94”</p>
<p>“哈哈哈哈哈哈哈你自己套路？”</p>
<p><img width="1024" height="1528" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/71db26cf494c49a3aeeff473e03cc634.jpeg"></p>
<p>2016年4月25号，追到了。</p>
<p>刚开始在一起的时候，懂事听话可爱，两个人去南京旅游才知道她到底多能吃。</p>
<p><img width="1024" height="1494" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/de849b8ff4b04aebb3ee5b45954a6c4e.jpeg"></p>
<p>两人在一起以后，每天各种合照▼</p>
<p><img width="900" height="800" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/54511115908b4b96942aebd583473563.jpeg"></p>
<p>两人一狗，就是最好的生活。</p>
<p><img width="1024" height="1820" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/c111e30d5173493b81ac215187b935ef.jpeg"></p>
<p>真实情感的生日长文了解一下▼</p>
<p>“我了解你的小脾气，懂得你的小心思，知道怎么哄你开心，也知道怎么让你生气。我从未费尽心机去了解你，但一切就顺其自然地来了。”</p>
<p><img width="1024" height="803" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/53a21e08e04349139b9e18b1d34f1ce7.jpeg"></p>
<p>一如庄庄的微博简介：微秃的一个八百线屠狗博主，两个人从恋爱开始就相亲相爱到现在。</p>
<p>在一起的画风是这样的，一言不合就亲亲抱抱▼</p>
<p><img width="1024" height="769" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/649d83485f30494bbf5aa93b2383b21d.jpeg"></p>
<p><img width="960" height="960" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/49d0c98cb50244d390269945ae9dad80.jpeg"></p>
<p>国际接吻日的三连击了解一下</p>
<p><img width="240" height="240" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/6f0395e9750d4e23a91bea1574ffaafc.gif"></p>
<p><img width="240" height="240" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/eca5650be675497f99c84d119d6b7800.gif"></p>
<p><img width="240" height="240" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/44fc119c968c44f5a60f2494165f83d4.gif"></p>
<p>互相在脸上画画</p>
<p><img width="1024" height="1024" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/0421ac932ab14afd877446570957b02c.jpeg"></p>
<p>把睡觉的男朋友当做拍照的参照物也是很顽皮</p>
<p><img width="708" height="1599" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/2a8deb0986394fcf95d014dcb035307c.jpeg"></p>
<p>两个人一起各种国家旅游打卡：韩国＋泰国＋土耳其▼</p>
<p><img width="750" height="998" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/91c4fa07c01a4ba7a155aee08bd3174d.jpeg"></p>
<p><img width="750" height="723" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/8db83a7cf4e74dc59c5e57ab201753b2.jpeg"></p>
<p><img width="750" height="765" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/9e64164e484d41e1a783b44a7d7a5d4e.jpeg"></p>
<p>更多时候，两个人的恋爱过程就是沙雕日常。</p>
<p><img width="690" height="690" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/af1134363ad240cabbdb348ebc679b34.jpeg"></p>
<p><img width="690" height="690" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/be9a7053d1ec4f57aedb457b6752aedf.jpeg"></p>
<p>大部分时候很沙雕：</p>
<p>两人一起去土耳其，庄庄讲老尚弱智，因为他被欧洲蚊子咬了很开心。</p>
<p><img width="750" height="567" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/fa60e1511cac4f2da93bfd91378f0cc7.jpeg"></p>
<p>放P这个事情也可以讲好多次▼</p>
<p><img width="750" height="347" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/ef8f9cc4d2574358989fdeb8caf8c58a.jpeg"></p>
<p>情侣生活在一起就是什么话题都没有顾忌▼</p>
<p><img width="750" height="352" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/0cb610ea38e84760a8e9bb329101f716.jpeg"></p>
<p>男友踩到狗屎也是让人非常开心的事情▼</p>
<p><img width="750" height="1003" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/67d7a4f9f9d2499f9a954e86e93b715a.jpeg"></p>
<p>老尚嫌弃庄庄有着80斤的脸、100斤的胳膊、100斤的腿、150斤的腰▼</p>
<p><img width="750" height="355" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/d481218471b84455b8f2cab6b902c001.jpeg"></p>
<p>“宝宝 要骑车去吗”</p>
<p>“好啊好啊”</p>
<p>“好吧那你自己骑吧 我开车”</p>
<p><img width="750" height="385" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/38f616f30ee3427ab5dded22d61ad751.jpeg"></p>
<p>老尚调闹钟就是为了叫醒自己，再让自己叫醒他。</p>
<p><img width="750" height="305" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/1607166533664429ae643502d659a3d9.jpeg"></p>
<p>老尚表示给自己选礼物很困难，因为看起来不适合那些高档的东西。</p>
<p><img width="750" height="254" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/3a2e3d257c774c24836b9322010d5cab.jpeg"></p>
<p>在停车场劈叉式摔倒，就被老尚笑了一天。</p>
<p><img width="750" height="377" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/86416158591c4df58289e0279b6309a9.jpeg"></p>
<p>邀请老尚一起打英雄联盟被嫌弃：我怕我骂你</p>
<p><img width="750" height="350" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/d07752529b2e441bb16025677991e48d.jpeg"></p>
<p>拍照的时候给自己开发了一个蹲着的动作，被嫌弃像癞蛤蟆起跳。</p>
<p><img width="750" height="351" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/316d8495737b418ab0eee7bfb1054fa8.jpeg"></p>
<p>老尚还公然表示自己要“家暴”</p>
<p><img width="750" height="296" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/27d72dea20604904b39e7b383bbc408f.jpeg"></p>
<p>老尚还嫌弃庄庄：别人网红的微博故事都是美景和美食，这位女朋友是唯一想靠男朋友颜值火起来的网红。</p>
<p><img width="750" height="1232" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/b6f3ab4214db4e05bd505f0352ae4d32.jpeg"></p>
<p>看看女朋友在男朋友的车里都放了什么：</p>
<p><img width="750" height="415" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/1c97354b07984f7fa163fdcc90aa664a.jpeg"></p>
<p><img width="1600" height="1600" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/4e6c3d4ba1464b64b51a289a188f5dc6.jpeg"></p>
<p><img width="1103" height="1105" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/fb9dff5122aa442c9a0b6317dfe2cb86.jpeg"></p>
<p><img width="1099" height="1100" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/f52f5d14756941a4a6746ee5e7587af2.jpeg"></p>
<p>但是偶尔又真的很甜：</p>
<p>庄庄问老尚其他女孩子的长相，只会得到“不知道反正都长一个样”的回答。</p>
<p><img width="750" height="348" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/9b1553747d6b4828b8bc00651fae663e.jpeg"></p>
<p>被岳父批评的话，那就先给个巴掌再给颗枣。</p>
<p><img width="750" height="642" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/9311418f0f0e4874b939ec97db0eb604.jpeg"></p>
<p>但是老尚母亲就超级护着庄庄，梦见儿子分手就要断绝关系，除了庄庄谁都不认儿媳妇。</p>
<p><img width="690" height="690" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/d02aad4acefc41dd90942cbbe970faa8.jpeg"></p>
<p>偶尔出现一点小争执，老尚还会公开发布检讨书。</p>
<p>第一次检讨是大年初二喝多了，忘记和女友讲回家，忘记和女友讲晚安，让她担心▼</p>
<p><img width="595" height="1428" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/7d0adfac0d6d4c4790749d2d02416032.jpeg"></p>
<p>第二次检讨书是打扑克没有回女友微信，没有践行不能超过两个小时不联系她的承诺。</p>
<p><img width="1024" height="1518" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/e7a0069cb53e45d783cd639768a355c8.jpeg"></p>
<p>这位哥们是有点话痨，不过这两份检讨堪称是优秀检讨示例了。</p>
<p><img width="960" height="960" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/73e5cd91e6944b608706afe4863dbe44.jpeg"></p>
<p>各种生日都在，各种纪念日都在，各种节日都在▼</p>
<p><img width="750" height="747" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/efbb94076fb84a1b9229150812c57449.jpeg"></p>
<p><img width="750" height="1028" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/35d7fcd50e2540049f8edfc0d88074d8.jpeg"></p>
<p>在一起两周年的时候，男友在网上买了气球和礼物。</p>
<p><img width="598" height="977" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/2b8a9e59eaad46f5912380976cef48fd.jpeg"></p>
<p>然后瞒着女友布置房间，就是为了给她一个巨大的惊喜。</p>
<p><img width="596" height="1009" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/4d74d1f31bfa418b8d8beb9cc3214bd8.jpeg"></p>
<p><img width="598" height="339" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/e4cf7bb063824295806e198a61a2c10d.jpeg"></p>
<p>他也是超级真诚：</p>
<p>有更多更美好的在等着我带你一起去完成</p>
<p>想象过无数次你在我面前穿上婚纱的样子</p>
<p>我们一起努力…希望我是新郎而不是伴郎</p>
<p><img width="750" height="1073" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/b7d7c7615fa04678a36cbc01bfaa38ee.jpeg"></p>
<p>两个人很认真地在一起，很认真向往未来，也经常开玩笑自己很小，没有结婚的打算。</p>
<p><img width="750" height="556" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/b1769333d8574dabac91a87282418a88.jpeg"></p>
<p><img width="750" height="340" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/43dd2d03f0a142c8825c2ee75a9da672.jpeg"></p>
<p><img width="750" height="788" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/b903e82cd135419e87944f8ed2790a06.jpeg"></p>
<p>但是吧，有时候婚姻就是这么水到渠成。</p>
<p><img width="690" height="517" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/7260599eda3a489ea176f06c2c46440c.jpeg"></p>
<p>对了，他们求婚的地方就在他们认识的同济大学，也是很绝。</p>
<p>你说说，两个人颜值不错，家境也不错，同济大学的成绩也很OK。</p>
<p>没有毕业就分手，而是继续打打闹闹，顺理成章开起了网红店铺，我觉得…………赚钱也很OK。</p>
<p>这样的两个人英年早婚了，那就只能苦着笑恭喜了。</p>
<p><img width="440" height="330" class="content-image" data-src="//5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20180910/68b8b52a29f74e2eb86d7bc11d0ec8c1.jpeg"></p>
<p>别人家的男朋友果然不会让人失望</p>
